SUMMARY:In Conversation with the Latin American Fiesta Association
LOCATION:401 West Kennedy Boulevard Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Lights\, camera\, action! Join the Henry B. Plant Museum for t
 he screening of the restored newsreel\, The 1970 Latin American Fiesta Ass
 ociation Tour. Following the film there will be a conversation with past L
 atin American Fiesta Association queens and court members. Artifacts for t
 he Latin America Fiesta Association are currently on view in the exhibit\,
  Gaspars Gold: Carnival and Community a New South City . Complimentary adm
 ission\, light refreshments. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/192
 121
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/192121
END:VEVENT
