 rapher and Syrian refugee Serbest Salih and his mobile darkroom that bring
 s photography to overlooked communities across Turkey\, where children con
 tend with access to school\, memory and displacement from devastating eart
 hquakes. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/192071
