SUMMARY:Lowry Park Central Community Organization
LOCATION:1100 Sligh Ave\, Tampa\, FL 33604 Tampa \, FL 33604 United States
DESCRIPTION:The Neighborhood Association will hold monthly meetings on the
  third Thursday of each month at 6:30 PM\, beginning in June and continuin
 g through the end of the year. These meetings are intended to encourage co
 mmunity involvement\, discuss neighborhood concerns\, promote safety initi
 atives\, and strengthen communication and collaboration among residents. \
